SixArm.com » Postfix » Scripts for mail server management

This repo has a few helpful Postfix scripts:

  * postfix-version        Show the Postfix mail version number
  * postfix-header-checks  Quick testing for anti-spam header expressions 
  * postfix-body-checks    Quick testing for anti-spam body expressions 

For more info please see documentation for postfix, postconf, postmap, etc.
